pull_request.title: OI-2538: Fix mail icon margin on partner page
pull_request.body: - Fixes margin on mail icon in partner page. I've tested this with other languages and the margin/spacing looks good. - I also updated the styles to use logical margin values i.e. margin inline/block instead of margin left(or right)/margin top(or bottom). ### Before ### After
